app_name: جديد اهنك مهستي بدون نت - Mahasty New Music
app_detail:
Do you like Mahasty music? You are in the right place, because you will listen to the best sounds of Mahasty for free! Choose your favorite classical music and enjoy! Choose from the full range of Mahasty free music !!!!!!
Eftekhar Dadehbala (Persian: افتخار دده‌بالا‎), better known as Mahasti (Persian: مهستی‎, 16 November 1946 – 25 June 2007), was an Iranian singer. She was the younger sister of singer Hayedeh.
Her albums include: 
1981: Parandeye Mohajer
1982: Tou Bezan ta Man Beraghsam
